<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[هـ‍]</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c4">[تَأَلَّه]</span>: التألُّه: التعبُّد.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>و <span class="c4">[تَأَلَّى]</span>: أي حلف.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وفي الحديث <span class="c2">«٣»</span>:<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c5">قال أبو جهل لابن مسعود رضي اللّاه عنه:</span><a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c5">واللّاه لأقتلنّك فقال له:</span> من يَتَأَلَّ على اللّاه يُكَذِّبْهُ.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
